everything. I’m still in shock about what’s happened.’

Witnesses
said they saw the workman, sent by South Gloucestershire social housing
provider Merlin Housing Society, using hot bitumen and a blowtorch to 
reline the concrete guttering on the house.

Ms
Phelps will now have to be re-homed. Merlin Housing meanwhile is now 
